---

<Layout
  title='Home'
  pageTitle='Home'
  description='My Portfolio website.'
>
<main class='bgc0 p-6'>
  <MobileSocials />

  <section id='about' class='grid grid-flow-row sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4 justify-stretch'>
    <h2 class='hidden'>About Brutal</h2>
    <div class='sm:col-span-2'>
      <Card colorIndex={4}>
        <div class='flex flex-col justify-between items-start gap-4'>
          <Hero client:load></Hero>
          
          <MyButton target={'_blank'} href={resume} tab_bg_color="white">
            View my resume &rarr;
          </MyButton>
        
        </div>
      </Card>
    </div>


    <div class="max-h-[300px]">

      <Image
		class="object-cover h-full w-full rounded-lg border-3 border-black card-shadow"
		src={headshot}
		alt="My headshot"
		width={headshot.width}
		height={headshot.height}
	/>
</div>
<div class='sm:col-span-3'>
  <Card colorIndex={4}>
    <h2 class='sanchez tc0 text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl mb-4 dm-serif'>
      Who am I?
    </h2>
    <p class='poppins tc1'>
     
      I hold a Master's degree in Data Analytics from the<b> University of Bolton</b> 
      and a Bachelor's degree in <em>Materials Engineering</em> from the University of Lagos. 
      Tools and frameworks in use in my work include machine learning libraries like
       TensorFlow and PyTorch, 
      for building robust data pipelines and predictive models.
      
    Outside of work, I find enjoyment in playing football to unwind after a long day of debugging.
    </p>
  </Card>
</div>
</section>
<RecentBlogPosts client:load/>
  </main>
</Layout>

